{
  "stem": "11552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what happened during the time, he had a very beautiful voice, and he was singing a-- from a-- from a-- from a play called It's about a village girl whose sweetheart went away, and she was singing her heart out to him, and then he was answering her.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- and I was in the same play during the Russian occupation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was Natalka.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then he was singing the boy's role, I was answering him as Natalka-- we were singing to each other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We never took, so-- when he said, Slavka, what are you doing among the Jews?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, he didn't know I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told him, I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he, you know, was shocked, and then he started clamoring to get a-- so I made my speech.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told him, I say, we are just women and children here, innocent people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I made my first speech and say, for the crime that you are going to commit here, I say to him, I swear on your God and my God, I will hunt you to the grave.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you ever have children, you will see my eyes in them in the crime that you will be committing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You will never be forgiven it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It will live with you, and our innocent blood will be on you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I kept talking and talking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And our eyes connected, and suddenly, it was very quiet and he motioned them out, and they left us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, we couldn't stay there anymore, and so I knew some-- some farmers who had barns, and-- and I led-- I knew which would be OK, so I told the people where to go.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I led them there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
